# Product catalog

This widget can be used for provisioning of virtual machines VM. The customised wizzard helps to do that very quickly.
User can choose from several prepared products - as from plain operation systems (Windows or Rethat) or web servers containing applications e.g. databases.

</p>

## Wizzard running

Preparred wizzard is designed for easy step-by-step going throught. There are following steps:

 - "General" with Product name, Quantity, Environment, Location, Network Segment
 - "Availability settings" - for selection whether the machine is to be placed in an availability set, availability zone or stay unassigned 
 - "SW configuration" - application configuration
 - "VM configuration" - define virtual machine size
 - "GSN"
